celebrity-spotlight-olaf.name: Celebrity Spotlight
celebrity-spotlight-olaf.summary: Stop by the Celebrity Spotlight at Disney’s Hollywood Studios to hang with your fave frosty friend from Disney's Frozen!

voyage-of-the-little-mermaid.name: Voyage of the Little Mermaid
voyage-of-the-little-mermaid.what_it_is: Musical stage show featuring characters from the Disney movie The Little Mermaid
voyage-of-the-little-mermaid.when_to_go: Before 9:45 a.m., just before closing, or use FASTPASS.
voyage-of-the-little-mermaid.probable_wait_time: Before 9:30 a.m., 10-30 minutes; after 9:30 a.m., 35-70 minutes
voyage-of-the-little-mermaid.summary: Immerse yourself in unforgettable moments of the hit animated film The Little Mermaid at this live-show puppetry extravaganza!

walt-disney-one-mans-dream.name: Walt Disney Presents
walt-disney-one-mans-dream.ultimate_task: Walk through exhibit and view full film.
walt-disney-one-mans-dream.summary: Explore Walt Disney’s legendary creative legacy through a fascinating multimedia journey that includes rare artifacts.

minnie-and-mickey-at-red-carpet-dreams.name: Mickey and Minnie Starring in Red Carpet Dreams
minnie-and-mickey-at-red-carpet-dreams.sort_name: mickey and minnie starring in red carpet dreams
minnie-and-mickey-at-red-carpet-dreams.summary: This classy couple is destined to see their names in lights—and sign autographs for adoring fans like you!

celebrate-with-incredibles-at-pixar-plac.name: Celebrate with the Incredibles at Pixar Place
celebrate-with-incredibles-at-pixar-plac.ultimate_task: Enjoy for 5 minutes or photo/autograph with one character.
celebrate-with-incredibles-at-pixar-plac.sort_name: celebrate with the incredibles at pixar place

fantasmic.name: Fantasmic!
fantasmic.probable_wait_time: 50-90 minutes for a seat; 35-40 minutes for standing room
fantasmic.summary: See the forces of good and evil battling it out in Mickey’s dream during this nighttime, outdoor extravagant musical.

citizens-of-hollywood.name: Citizens of Hollywood
citizens-of-hollywood.ultimate_task: View for 5 minutes. Each show with a distinct group of characters counts as a separate attraction.

jedi-training-academy.name: Jedi Training: Trials of the Temple
jedi-training-academy.sort_name: jedi training trials of the temple
jedi-training-academy.summary: Watch younglings train in the ways of the Force and put their skills to the test against the Dark Side.

star-wars-galaxy-far-far-away.name: Star Wars: A Galaxy Far, Far Away
star-wars-galaxy-far-far-away.sort_name: star wars a galaxy far far away
star-wars-galaxy-far-far-away.summary: Witness the power of a live show that brings legendary scenes from the Star Wars films to life!

star-wars-launch-bay-encounter-darth-vad.name: Star Wars Launch Bay: Encounter Darth Vader
star-wars-launch-bay-encounter-darth-vad.ultimate_task: Meet 1 character at Launch Bay. Get photo and autograph.
star-wars-launch-bay-encounter-darth-vad.sort_name: star wars launch bay encounter darth vader
star-wars-launch-bay-encounter-darth-vad.summary: Prepare yourself for an epic run-in with the Dark Lord of the Sith.

star-wars-launch-bay.name: Star Wars Launch Bay
star-wars-launch-bay.what_it_is: Movie Trailer, Props, and Character Greetings
star-wars-launch-bay.ultimate_task: Explore for 15 minutes or meet 1 character.
star-wars-launch-bay.summary: Check out props and models from Star Wars: The Last Jedi, play games, snap photos, screen videos, and greet heroes and villains.

lightning-mcqueens-racing-academy.name: Lightning McQueen's Racing Academy
lightning-mcqueens-racing-academy.summary: Get pumped for a high-octane, first-of-its-kind show that'll put you right in the middle of the Disney and Pixar Cars universe.

wonderful-world-animation.name: Wonderful World of Animation
wonderful-world-animation.summary: This excitement-packed projection show will take you on an incredible journey through more than 90 years of Disney and Pixar animation.

rise-of-the-resistance.name: Star Wars: Rise of the Resistance
rise-of-the-resistance.sort_name: star wars rise of the resistance
rise-of-the-resistance.summary: Join the Resistance in an epic battle against the First Order on this exciting new ride—now open!

indiana-jones-epic-stunt-spectacular.name: Indiana Jones Epic Stunt Spectacular!
indiana-jones-epic-stunt-spectacular.when_to_go: First two shows or last evening show
indiana-jones-epic-stunt-spectacular.summary: Cheer on Indy and Marion as they perform amazing stunts with blazing special effects to demonstrate movie-making magic.

slinky-dog-dash.name: Slinky Dog Dash
slinky-dog-dash.when_to_go: As soon as the park opens, during meals, or in the last hour the park is open
slinky-dog-dash.summary: Take off on a family-friendly coaster as Slinky Dog’s coils twist around curves, hills and drops

bb-8-astromech-on-duty.name: BB-8 Astromech on Duty
bb-8-astromech-on-duty.summary: Say hello to this excitable sidekick at Star Wars Launch Bay before he takes off on another important mission.

alien-swirling-saucers.name: Alien Swirling Saucers
alien-swirling-saucers.when_to_go: First or Last Hour the Park is Open
alien-swirling-saucers.summary: Board your toy rocket and hang on tight as the Aliens take you on a spin through space

millennium-falcon-smugglers-run.name: Millennium Falcon: Smugglers Run
millennium-falcon-smugglers-run.summary: Fly the Millennium Falcon on a thrilling interactive smuggling mission—now open.

tower-of-terror.name: The Twilight Zone Tower of Terror
tower-of-terror.when_to_go: First or last 30 minutes park is open or use Fastpass.
tower-of-terror.summary: Hurtle up and down aboard a haunted, elevator-themed ride. You’re about to enter… The Twilight Zone!

toy-story-mania.name: Toy Story Mania!
toy-story-mania.when_to_go: As soon as the park opens, or use FastPass+
toy-story-mania.summary: Ride 'n' blast moving targets at this midway-style, 4D shootin’ game starring popular characters—only at Toy Story Land!

star-tours.name: Star Tours: The Adventures Continue
star-tours.when_to_go: Before 10 a.m., after 6 p.m., or use FASTPASS.
star-tours.summary: Make the jump to hyperspace as you ride aboard a 3D, motion-simulated space flight to popular destinations from Star Wars.

rock-n-roller-coaster.name: Rock 'n' Roller Coaster Starring Aerosmith
rock-n-roller-coaster.when_to_go: First 30 minutes that park is open or use Fastpass.
rock-n-roller-coaster.sort_name: rock n roller coaster starring aerosmith
rock-n-roller-coaster.summary: Race through the darkened freeways of Los Angeles in a super-stretch limo to the rockin' tunes of Aerosmith.

muppet-vision-3d.name: Muppet*Vision 3D
muppet-vision-3d.ultimate_task: View full show. Pre-show not required.
muppet-vision-3d.summary: Experience the magic of the Muppets during a hilarious, eye-popping film and live-action extravaganza.

meet-chewbacca.name: Star Wars Launch Bay: Meet Chewbacca
meet-chewbacca.sort_name: star wars launch bay meet chewbacca
meet-chewbacca.summary: Get ready for a rebel rendezvous with this legendary Wookiee warrior.

jingle-bell-jingle-bam.name: Jingle Bell, Jingle BAM!
jingle-bell-jingle-bam.summary: Jingle Bell, Jingle BAM! is a holiday nighttime spectacular involving projections, fireworks, seasonal music, and snow.

frozen-sing-along-celebration.name: For the First Time In Forever: A Frozen Sing-Along Celebration
frozen-sing-along-celebration.sort_name: for the first time in forever a frozen singalong celebration
frozen-sing-along-celebration.summary: Delight as Frozen springs to life in this lively retelling—packed with a flurry of stories, songs and sing-alongs.

beauty-and-the-beast-live-on-stage.name: Beauty and the Beast - Live on Stage
beauty-and-the-beast-live-on-stage.sort_name: beauty and the beast live on stage
beauty-and-the-beast-live-on-stage.summary: Be swept into the romantic fairy tale of the Beast who could only be saved by love in this lavish Broadway-style musical!

star-wars-galactic-spectacular.name: Star Wars: A Galactic Spectacular
star-wars-galactic-spectacular.what_it_is: Fireworks and Projections with Star Wars Music
star-wars-galactic-spectacular.summary: Conclude your day in a galaxy far, far away with an all-new nighttime spectacular bursting with memorable Star Wars moments.

mickey-minnies-runaway-railway.name: Mickey & Minnie's Runaway Railway
mickey-minnies-runaway-railway.when_to_go: As soon as the park opens, or in the last hour the park is open
mickey-minnies-runaway-railway.summary: Zip away on a zany adventure through a cartoon universe crammed with surprises.

mickey-shorts-theater.name: Vacation Fun - An Original Animated Short with Mickey & Minnie
mickey-shorts-theater.sort_name: vacation fun  an original animated short with mickey  minnie
mickey-shorts-theater.summary: Get star struck at Disney’s Hollywood Studios when you join your best pals for a one-of-a-kind animated short featuring everyone’s favorite mouse and his leading lady.

disney-movie-magic.name: Disney Movie Magic
disney-movie-magic.summary: Relive your favorite moments in cinema with classic projections that feature the magic of Disney.
